# Botticelli bots

## What's it

The main idea is to provide a simple bot creation and support platform.

Botticelli allows you to develop cross-platform bots with common business logic.

The main features are:

    cross-platform (Windows/Linux are supported)
    supports different messengers
    supports AI integration
    supports message brokers integration (such as RabbitMq)
    supports scheduling
    supports bot managing
    supports bot monitoring

